title: God of War HD [PS3] [PSN]
description:
God of War HD for ps3.
US version NPUA80490.

I can confirm it to work on Rebug 4.46.


To install

1. Install god of war and reactpsn.(Unless of course you already have reactpsn)

2. Place "exdata" folder on flash drive.

3. Put flash drive in the right usb port.

4. Create a user new user and name it "aa".

5. Run reactpsn and do not press any buttons.

6. Play the game!
